description: Caliente Grill is heating things up on the San Antonio streets with their delicious grilled Mexican dishes. Scrumptiously cheesy Carne Asada Fries, crispy & spicy Bacon-Wrapped Jalapeños, tasty Cod Fish Tacos (with mango habanero salsa and creamy cilantro avocado sauce) are just a few of the amazing Caliente creations you’ll find on their crazy-cool menu. For all this and much more, call on Caliente Grill to come cater your next event or just come on out and eat!
name: Caliente Grill
